Akamai’s Environmental Management System
Our environmental management system (EMS) has been verified by a third party as compliant with the ISO 14001:2015 standard. We have implemented a range of tracking, monitoring, measuring, and reporting systems internally to meet all aspects of the standard, uniquely apply it to Akamai, and establish an evolving EMS.
