here
.
The Privacy Policy applies when you visit our website, download our app, apply for and use your Clearpay account, or otherwise interact and engage with us in relation to our customer products, features, and services as set out in the Privacy Policy.
“Personal Information” is information that reasonably identifies you and is about you, directly or indirectly as described under applicable privacy laws in countries we operate in. Personal information does not include information that has been made anonymous and cannot reasonably identify a specific person.
